{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-408-admissible-paths-through-a-grid","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 408: Dozvoljeni putevi kroz mrežu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Neka se tačka rešetke ($x$, $y$) naziva neprihvatljivom ako su $x$, $y$ i $x + y$ svi pozitivni savršeni kvadrati.</p>\n<p>Na primer, (9, 16) nije prihvaćen, dok (0, 4), (3, 1) i (9, 4) ne postoje.</p>\n<p>Razmotrite put od tačke ($x_1$, $y_1$) do tačke ($x_2$, $y_2$) koristeći samo jedinične korake ka severu ili istoku. Takav put nazovimo prihvatljivim ako nijedna njegova međutačka nije prihvatljiva.</p>\n<p>Neka je $P(n)$ broj prihvatljivih puteva od (0, 0) do ($n$, $n$). Dokazano je da $P(5) = 252$, $P(16) = 596\\,994\\,440$ i $P(1\\,000)\\bmod 1\\,000\\,000\\,007 = 341\\,920\\,854$.</p>\n<p>Izračunaj $P(10\\,000\\,000)\\bmod 1\\,000\\,000\\,007$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5091000cf542c51001b","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302076,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-408-admissible-paths-through-a-grid"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function admissiblePaths() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nadmissiblePaths();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>admissiblePaths()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>299742733</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(admissiblePaths(), 299742733);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-